    <Label name="lblDescription" id="48f38faa-64bf-4afc-ae5f-50c527c15972">
        <caption>To include a Test Message in this Web Test, select the "Available" Test Message, then click the "&amp;Insert" button.  Note that a Test Message can be included in the Web Test multiple times.  To insert the Test Message above or below an already included message, select the "Included" Message, then choose the "Abo&amp;ve/Top" or "&amp;Below/End" option and click the "&amp;Insert" button.  To remove a Test Message from the Web Test, select the "Included" Message, then click the "&amp;Remove" button.</caption>
        <wordWrap/>
        <fontSize>8.25</fontSize>
        <foreColor>-2147483640</foreColor>
